Feels like a promise.

65
00:06:30,058 --> 00:06:31,392
So, this is my vow.

66
00:06:34,687 --> 00:06:36,481
All gods will die.

67
00:07:21,984 --> 00:07:24,320
Come, come, gather round.

68
00:07:24,487 --> 00:07:27,698
