<i>on a Woman Wolf.</i>

80
00:08:10,616 --> 00:08:13,494
<i>But Thor's one true love</i>
<i>was an Earth woman</i>

81
00:08:13,578 --> 00:08:15,246
<i>named Jane Fonda.</i>

82
00:08:15,329 --> 00:08:17,790
<i>Oh, wait. No. Jane Foster.</i>

83
00:08:17,874 --> 00:08:21,627
<i>But sadly, in the battle</i>
<i>for love, Thor lost.</i>

84
00:08:21,711 --> 00:08:22,503
<i>Ooh.</i>

85
00:08:23,462 --> 00:08:26,424
<i>In fact, he lost a lot</i>
<i>of people in those days.</i>

86
00:08:26,591 --> 00:08:27,675
<i>His mum.</i>

87
00:08:27,758 --> 00:08:29,468
<i>His dad.</i>

88
00:08:29,552 --> 00:08:30,386
<i>And that guy.</i>

89
00:08:30,469 --> 00:08:31,637
<i>And that guy.</i>

90
00:08:31,721 --> 00:08:33,055
<i>And whoever that is.</i>

91
00:08:33,139 --> 00:08:34,265
<i>And Heimdall.</i>

92
00:08:34,432 --> 00:08:36,184
<i>And his brother.</i>

93
00:08:36,267 --> 00:08:37,935
<i>And his brother, again.</i>

94
00:08:38,019 --> 00:08:39,020
<i>And again.</i>

95
00:08:40,980 --> 00:08:43,274
<i>Poor Thor had to watch</i>
<i>his planet explode.</i>

96
00:08:43,983 --> 00:08:46,194
<i>And then he said, "What have I done?"</i>

97
00:08:46,944 --> 00:08:48,237
<i>It seemed that everything</i>

98
00:08:48,321 --> 00:08:50,239
<i>and everyone he loved, he lost.</i>

99
00:08:50,406 --> 00:08:53,284
<i>And so he hid his heart</i>
<i>behind a big, fleshy bod,</i>

100
00:08:53,451 --> 00:08:55,870
<i>so it could never be broken again.</i>

101
00:08:56,412 --> 00:08:58,247
<i>But just because he was done loving,</i>

102
00:08:58,331 --> 00:08:59,957
<i>didn't mean he was done fighting.</i>

103
00:09:00,875 --> 00:09:03,711
<i>He teamed up with</i>
<i>the Guardians of the Galaxy</i>

104
00:09:03,878 --> 00:09:06,297
<i>and set off on some</i>
<i>classic Thor adventures.</i>

105
00:09:06,923 --> 00:09:08,716
<i>He got in shape.</i>

106
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,301
<i>Putting in the hard yards.</i>

107
00:09:10,468 --> 00:09:14,472
<i>Turning pains into gains,</i>
<i>and never skipping leg day.</i>

108
00:09:15,932 --> 00:09:18,893
<i>He went from Dad Bod to God Bod.</i>

109
00:09:18,976 --> 00:09:22,271
<i>But beneath his God Bod,</i>
<i>there was still a Sad Bod</i>

110
00:09:22,355 --> 00:09:23,522
<i>just trying to get out.</i>

111
00:09:26,067 --> 00:09:27,276
<i>Because all of the bods</i>

112
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,445
<i>that Thor had worn over the years</i>

113
00:09:29,612 --> 00:09:30,738
<i>couldn't hide the pain</i>

114
00:09:30,821 --> 00:09:32,698
<i>that he was feeling on the inside.</i>

115
00:09:34,575 --> 00:09:36,452
<i>So he gave up his search for love,</i>

116
00:09:37,453 --> 00:09:40,331
<i>accepting that he was</i>
<i>only good for one thing...</i>

117
00:09:41,582 --> 00:09:44,752
<i>Waiting in quiet contemplation</i>
<i>for someone to say,</i>

118
00:09:44,835 --> 00:09:48,506
<i>"Thor, we need your help</i>
<i>to win this battle."</i>

119
00:09:49,924 --> 00:09:51,300
Thor.

120
00:09:51,384 --> 00:09:53,344
