146
00:11:01,871 --> 00:11:03,080
Well, as they say,

147
00:11:03,164 --> 00:11:04,582
"Better late than not at all."

148
00:11:04,665 --> 00:11:06,375
Yes, it's very nice.

149
00:11:06,542 --> 00:11:09,587
As you know, we used to live
in a peaceful oasis.

150
00:11:09,754 --> 00:11:11,672
But then our gods were murdered.

151
00:11:11,756 --> 00:11:12,715
Murdered?

152
00:11:12,798 --> 00:11:15,926
And now our sacred temple
has been left unguarded,

153
00:11:16,010 --> 00:11:18,721
and Habooska's hordes
took control of its power.

154
00:11:18,804 --> 00:11:22,350
