Yeah, but now you understand wormholes.

197
00:15:26,719 --> 00:15:27,845
Watch those movies.

198
00:15:27,928 --> 00:15:29,471
- Okay.
- Okay.

199
00:15:29,555 --> 00:15:31,807
Saw the Hot Cheetos, had to get it.

200
