234
00:17:22,584 --> 00:17:25,921
<i>Results are</i>
<i>still coming back the same.</i>

235
00:17:26,505 --> 00:17:28,424
<i>I'm afraid the chemo</i>
<i>has very little effect.</i>

236
00:17:30,759 --> 00:17:32,219
<i>I'm so sorry, Jane.</i>

237
00:17:33,595 --> 00:17:34,805
<i>If there's anything I can do,</i>

238
00:17:34,888 --> 00:17:36,807
<i>or if you just wanna talk, call me.</i>

239
00:18:31,528 --> 00:18:34,615
Smell like a king,
because you're worthy.

240
00:18:34,948 --> 00:18:36,158
Old Spice.

241
00:18:38,619 --> 00:18:40,078
Cut!

242
00:19:07,189 --> 00:19:09,691
Look at this place.
It's beautiful.

243
00:19:09,775 --> 00:19:11,026
Home.

244
00:19:11,193 --> 00:19:12,361
Yes, home, Father.

245
00:19:12,986 --> 00:19:14,530
We're here to take you home.

246
00:19:14,613 --> 00:19:17,407
Yes. To planet Asgard.

247
00:19:17,491 --> 00:19:19,952
Asgard is not a planet, my sons.

248
00:19:20,035 --> 00:19:22,496
It is people. It is you!

249
00:19:22,579 --> 00:19:24,873
And now, it is time

250
00:19:24,957 --> 00:19:27,584
for me to pass on to the spirit realm.

251
00:19:30,295 --> 00:19:32,047
I will take my place

252
00:19:32,214 --> 00:19:35,092
in the great banqueting hall
of Valhalla,

253
00:19:35,259 --> 00:19:37,678
the resting place of the gods.

254
