or some meaningless dalliance,

1304
01:10:34,857 --> 01:10:36,191
which only serves to numb the pain

1305
01:10:36,275 --> 01:10:37,359
instead of bringing you

1306
01:10:37,443 --> 01:10:38,903
real happiness or satisfaction?

1307
01:10:39,069 --> 01:10:42,448
- Yeah. Something like that.
- Hmm.

1308
01:10:44,199 --> 01:10:47,077
Beautiful. Beautiful things.

1309
01:10:51,040 --> 01:10:52,374
Jane.

1310
01:10:52,833 --> 01:10:53,834
Thor.

1311
01:10:53,918 --> 01:10:55,294
I wanna feel shitty about you.

1312
01:10:55,377 --> 01:10:56,462
What?

1313
01:11:00,466 --> 01:11:02,593
I wanna feel shitty about something

1314
01:11:02,676 --> 01:11:04,178
and I think that's you.

1315
01:11:04,261 --> 01:11:05,304
Not really getting any better.

1316
01:11:05,387 --> 01:11:06,972
It's not, is it? Damn it.

1317
01:11:07,222 --> 01:11:08,515
I wanna...

1318
01:11:08,599 --> 01:11:11,268
My friend, he told me that
it's better to feel shitty

1319
01:11:12,561 --> 01:11:14,480
from losing love than it is
to never experience love

1320
01:11:14,563 --> 01:11:16,065
and to feel nothing at all,
to feel empty,

1321
01:11:16,148 --> 01:11:17,316
and I think he was right,

1322
01:11:18,192 --> 01:11:20,611
which is how I've been feeling
for a long time.

1323
01:11:20,778 --> 01:11:23,072
I've pushed people away,
kept them at a distance

1324
01:11:23,155 --> 01:11:24,531
because of the fear of that loss,

1325
01:11:24,615 --> 01:11:25,491
but I don't wanna do that anymore.

1326
01:11:25,574 --> 01:11:26,825
I don't wanna live like that.

1327
01:11:26,909 --> 01:11:28,619
Better to close off your heart
than feel the pain.

1328
01:11:28,702 --> 01:11:30,871
That's what I did, yes.
I closed off my heart

1329
01:11:30,955 --> 01:11:32,831
and... and I meditated. Did you meditate?

1330
01:11:32,915 --> 01:11:34,208
No. It's so boring.

1331
01:11:34,291 --> 01:11:36,460
It actually made me more angry.

1332
01:11:36,961 --> 01:11:39,672
But I'm tired of giving myself
over to the idea of fate

1333
01:11:39,755 --> 01:11:41,632
and trying to figure out what
the universe wants from me.

1334
01:11:41,715 --> 01:11:43,092
I wanna live in the moment,

1335
01:11:43,175 --> 01:11:44,551
I wanna live like there's no tomorrow,

1336
01:11:44,635 --> 01:11:45,886
throw caution to the wind. I want...

1337
01:11:45,970 --> 01:11:48,013
- I wanna be with you, Jane.
- Ah.

1338
01:11:48,889 --> 01:11:49,723
What do you say?

1339
01:11:50,557 --> 01:11:52,309
I have cancer.

1340
01:11:54,687 --> 01:11:55,729
I'm sorry, what?

1341
01:11:56,313 --> 01:11:57,356
I'm sick.

1342
01:11:57,439 --> 01:11:59,108
- Wait. What's happening?
- Bye.

1343
01:11:59,400 --> 01:12:01,485
- Uh...
- No, no, no. Jane, Jane, Jane.

1344
01:12:01,568 --> 01:12:02,861
- Wait, wait, wait. Jane.
- What did I say?

1345
01:12:02,945 --> 01:12:04,863
I didn't mean that. Just kidding.

1346
01:12:04,947 --> 01:12:05,948
I...

1347
01:12:06,490 --> 01:12:08,117
don't have cancer.

1348
01:12:08,200 --> 01:12:09,660
Let's go smash something.

1349
01:12:10,411 --> 01:12:11,453
Jane, I'm so sorry.

1350
01:12:11,537 --> 01:12:13,539
Don't be sorry for me.

1351
01:12:15,124 --> 01:12:16,625
When did you find out?

1352
01:12:17,334 --> 01:12:18,711
Um...

1353
01:12:18,794 --> 01:12:20,587
Like six months ago.

1354
01:12:20,754 --> 01:12:22,840
I was just feeling tired, and then

1355
01:12:22,923 --> 01:12:24,550
they told me I have Stage Four.

1356
01:12:24,717 --> 01:12:26,427
Get my affairs in order.

1357
01:12:27,261 --> 01:12:29,680
And then I heard Mjolnir calling me,

1358
01:12:30,389 --> 01:12:32,933
so I thought maybe,
if science isn't working,

1359
01:12:33,767 --> 01:12:37,187
maybe Viking space magic.

1360
01:12:37,271 --> 01:12:38,814
That's why you came to New Asgard.

1361
01:12:38,897 --> 01:12:41,775
Yeah, I thought the hammer
maybe could cure me,

1362
01:12:41,942 --> 01:12:44,862
and I think it's getting better.

1363
01:12:45,529 --> 01:12:46,989
Maybe not.

1364
01:12:48,032 --> 01:12:50,242
Jane, none of us know how long we have.

1365
01:12:50,409 --> 01:12:52,661
We don't know what tomorrow holds.

1366
01:12:52,828 --> 01:12:53,829
And Mjolnir...

1367
01:12:54,204 --> 01:12:55,497
Mjolnir chose you.

1368
01:12:56,331 --> 01:12:58,208
And it chose you because you're worthy.

1369
01:12:58,375 --> 01:12:59,626
And that's something.

1370
01:12:59,793 --> 01:13:01,003
When I first met you,

1371
01:13:01,587 --> 01:13:02,588
I was unworthy.

1372
01:13:02,671 --> 01:13:04,214
I was unable to pick up that hammer.

1373
01:13:05,090 --> 01:13:06,258
But you taught me

1374
01:13:06,425 --> 01:13:09,386
there is no greater purpose
than to help those in need.

1375
01:13:10,137 --> 01:13:12,222
You made me worthy.

1376
01:13:13,682 --> 01:13:15,851
So whatever you wanna do,
we can do together.

1377
01:13:18,062 --> 01:13:19,104
Okay.

1378
01:13:19,188 --> 01:13:20,981
Now what do you wanna do?

1379
01:13:22,107 --> 01:13:24,777
I wanna get those children
back to their families.

1380
01:13:24,943 --> 01:13:26,236
I wanna finish that mission.

1381
01:13:27,404 --> 01:13:29,031
- Spoken like a true Thor.
- Hmm.

1382
01:13:30,616 --> 01:13:31,992
How do you feel now?

1383
01:13:33,160 --> 01:13:34,286
So scared.

1384
01:13:35,579 --> 01:13:36,538
How are you feeling?

1385
01:13:36,705 --> 01:13:37,998
Shitty.

1386
01:13:38,082 --> 01:13:39,041
How shitty?

1387
01:13:39,124 --> 01:13:40,751
- Really shitty.
- Well, then...

1388
01:13:51,887 --> 01:13:53,972
I wonder what those two
are talking about out there.

1389
01:13:54,556 --> 01:13:57,101
- Yeah, they're not talking.
- Oh!

1390
01:13:58,393 --> 01:14:00,062
Do you think those two
will ever hold hands

1391
