over a hot lava pool
and make a Thor baby?

1392
01:14:04,691 --> 01:14:06,860
It's unlikely, sadly.

1393
01:14:06,944 --> 01:14:08,654
Mm, that's too bad.

1394
01:14:08,737 --> 01:14:10,197
I think Thor would make a great dad.

1395
01:14:13,784 --> 01:14:14,785
Hey. We're here.

1396
01:14:23,710 --> 01:14:25,295
Where did all the colour go?

1397
01:14:58,579 --> 01:14:59,997
They're not here.

1398
01:15:05,586 --> 01:15:06,628
