01:15:55,886 --> 01:15:57,971
Bifrost is the key?

1401
01:16:07,189 --> 01:16:08,607
It's a trap!

1402
01:16:25,916 --> 01:16:27,125
You wanna tell me
why you just threw

1403
01:16:27,209 --> 01:16:28,377
Stormbreaker out the window?

1404
01:16:28,543 --> 01:16:30,671
He needs it to open
the Gates of Eternity.

1405
01:17:01,994 --> 01:17:03,662
We really have to
stop meeting like this.

1406
01:17:03,745 --> 01:17:04,871
Call the axe.

1407
01:17:04,955 --> 01:17:06,540
I'll call the axe
when you call the dentist.

1408
01:17:06,623 --> 01:17:09,334
Call the axe.

1409
01:17:09,418 --> 01:17:11,920
Tell me where the children are
or I'm gonna kill you.

1410
01:17:18,468 --> 01:17:19,970
Call the axe.

1411
01:17:27,144 --> 01:17:29,021
Some god you are.

1412
01:17:29,855 --> 01:17:33,233
You know nothing of being a god.

1413
01:17:35,694 --> 01:17:40,449
You went to the gods for help,
and they did nothing.

1414
01:17:40,532 --> 01:17:43,368
We're alike in that sense.

1415
01:17:43,452 --> 01:17:45,037
He's nothing like you.

1416
01:17:45,120 --> 01:17:46,621
What was that?

1417
01:17:49,791 --> 01:17:51,585
I said he's nothing like you.

1418
01:17:51,752 --> 01:17:53,128
That's right.

1419
01:17:53,295 --> 01:17:57,758
I'm not a hypocrite.
I'm truly creating peace.

1420
01:17:57,841 --> 01:17:59,676
Peace? You're murdering innocent gods.

1421
01:17:59,760 --> 01:18:00,886
Innocent?

1422
01:18:01,928 --> 01:18:03,055
Are you a Valkyrie?

1423
01:18:03,138 --> 01:18:04,139
Yes.

1424
01:18:04,222 --> 01:18:06,808
How exciting!

1425
01:18:07,934 --> 01:18:10,937
Oh, the gods failed you, too,

1426
01:18:11,271 --> 01:18:15,150
when your sisterhood
was led to slaughter.

1427
01:18:15,233 --> 01:18:16,318
Don't you dare speak...

1428
01:18:17,110 --> 01:18:19,237
Did you pray to the gods

1429
01:18:19,321 --> 01:18:23,533
when the women you loved
laid dying on the battlefield?

1430
01:18:25,327 --> 01:18:27,454
Did you beg them for help

1431
01:18:28,121 --> 01:18:30,248
as your family was massacred?

1432
