This one.

1434
01:18:39,216 --> 01:18:41,385
You're interesting.

1435
01:18:42,552 --> 01:18:44,054
You're different.

1436
01:18:44,679 --> 01:18:45,889
Yes.

1437
01:18:48,475 --> 01:18:50,602
Aw.

1438
