1443
01:19:10,914 --> 01:19:13,625
But it did nothing to change your fate.

1444
01:19:14,626 --> 01:19:17,754
The gods will use you,

1445
01:19:18,630 --> 01:19:21,425
but they will not help you.

1446
01:19:22,008 --> 01:19:26,930
There is no eternal reward for us.

1447
01:19:33,645 --> 01:19:35,063
She'll be gone soon.

1448
01:19:36,857 --> 01:19:38,650
And you know who won't help her?

1449
01:19:38,733 --> 01:19:40,569
I'll give you one guess.

1450
01:19:51,830 --> 01:19:53,165
I know your pain.

1451
01:19:53,248 --> 01:19:55,333
Love is pain.

1452
01:19:59,880 --> 01:20:02,299
I had a daughter once.

1453
01:20:03,133 --> 01:20:05,093
I put my faith in a higher power

1454
01:20:05,260 --> 01:20:07,971
hoping it would save her,

1455
01:20:08,138 --> 01:20:09,806
and she...

1456
01:20:11,016 --> 01:20:12,726
died.

1457
01:20:16,771 --> 01:20:18,940
Now I understand.

1458
01:20:19,024 --> 01:20:21,276
My daughter is the lucky one.

1459
01:20:21,902 --> 01:20:27,115
She does not have to grow up
in a world of suffering

1460
01:20:27,282 --> 01:20:28,783
and pain

1461
01:20:28,950 --> 01:20:33,205
run by wicked gods.

1462
01:20:35,081 --> 01:20:37,250
Choose love.

1463
01:20:38,376 --> 01:20:41,838
Call the axe.

1464
01:20:50,514 --> 01:20:52,557
Call

1465
01:20:52,933 --> 01:20:54,434
the axe.

1466
01:21:30,637 --> 01:21:31,888
You okay?

1467
01:21:32,055 --> 01:21:33,223
Yeah.

1468
01:21:35,850 --> 01:21:37,143
Mm, I wanna kill this guy.

1469
01:21:37,310 --> 01:21:39,771
So do I, but we have to take him alive.

1470
01:21:39,938 --> 01:21:42,023
He's our only link
to finding those children.

1471
01:22:56,014 --> 01:22:57,641
Oh! Thank you, Mr Goat.

1472
01:23:29,506 --> 01:23:31,549
Val!

1473
01:23:42,435 --> 01:23:44,062
We gotta get her out of here!

1474
01:23:53,780 --> 01:23:55,115
Hey. I got you.

1475
01:24:05,917 --> 01:24:08,086
Hey, guys, we're here.
Come on, let's go.

1476
01:24:08,169 --> 01:24:10,338
Stormbreaker, take us home.

1477
01:25:05,769 --> 01:25:08,021
...at a rate that
none of us have seen before.

1478
01:25:08,104 --> 01:25:09,606
Look, there are other more

1479
01:25:09,689 --> 01:25:11,566
aggressive forms of treatment
we can try,

1480
01:25:11,649 --> 01:25:12,734
but something's affecting

1481
01:25:12,817 --> 01:25:14,778
her body's ability to fight the cancer.

1482
01:25:15,612 --> 01:25:17,238
I'm sorry, Thor.

1483
01:25:31,044 --> 01:25:32,921
Oh, there you are. Okay.

1484
01:25:33,004 --> 01:25:34,130
What's goin' on out there?

1485
01:25:34,214 --> 01:25:36,174
Oh, some moron made
a fridge without a door.

1486
01:25:36,257 --> 01:25:37,258
Can you believe it?

1487
01:25:37,342 --> 01:25:38,384
Not to worry. Got it open

1488
01:25:38,468 --> 01:25:40,303
and got you all sorts of goodies.

1489
01:25:40,470 --> 01:25:41,596
How's Val?

1490
01:25:41,679 --> 01:25:44,098
Oh, she's in a lot of pain,
uh, but she is stable.

1491
01:25:44,182 --> 01:25:45,308
Okay, good.

1492
01:25:45,391 --> 01:25:48,311
Now you just gotta get this out of my...

1493
01:25:48,394 --> 01:25:49,938
Oh, no, no, no.
That's gotta stay in there.

1494
01:25:50,021 --> 01:25:51,898
That's all the magic potions and elixirs

1495
01:25:51,981 --> 01:25:53,233
doing their thing, so...

1496
01:25:53,316 --> 01:25:54,943
I'm just gonna pop out for a moment,

1497
01:25:55,026 --> 01:25:56,694
pick up the kids, kill the bad guy,

1498
01:25:56,778 --> 01:25:57,904
and then I'll come straight back.

1499
01:25:58,988 --> 01:26:00,657
You're going without me?

1500
01:26:01,241 --> 01:26:02,325
Uh, yeah.

1501
01:26:02,492 --> 01:26:04,536
What happened to, like,
doing everything together?

1502
01:26:04,619 --> 01:26:06,538
He's gonna use those kids
to distract you.

1503
01:26:06,621 --> 01:26:07,622
You need me.

1504
01:26:07,705 --> 01:26:09,791
I do need you, Jane. I need you alive.

1505
01:26:09,874 --> 01:26:11,751
It'd be great to have you
on the battlefield,

1506
01:26:11,835 --> 01:26:13,419
fighting Gorr side by side,

1507
01:26:13,503 --> 01:26:15,380
but that hammer is killing you.

1508
01:26:16,589 --> 01:26:17,632
Every time you use it,

1509
01:26:17,715 --> 01:26:19,592
