all of your mortal strength,

1510
01:26:19,759 --> 01:26:22,053
leaving your body
unable to fight the cancer.

1511
01:26:22,720 --> 01:26:24,764
What happened to,
"Live like there's no tomorrow"?

1512
01:26:24,848 --> 01:26:26,683
Well, that's before I knew
you might not have one.

1513
01:26:26,850 --> 01:26:28,268
Why not have one more adventure?

1514
01:26:28,476 --> 01:26:30,186
Jane, if there's a chance to live,
you have to take it.

1515
01:26:30,770 --> 01:26:33,690
Spoken like a true Thor
who does not have cancer.

1516
01:26:37,110 --> 01:26:39,737
I know I seem like
some cool astrophysicist

1517
01:26:39,821 --> 01:26:41,072
from New Mexico,

1518
01:26:41,155 --> 01:26:43,908
just living the dream, but look at me.

1519
01:26:43,992 --> 01:26:47,871
I wanna keep fighting.
I'm the Mighty Thor.

1520
01:26:47,954 --> 01:26:49,038
And you want me not to do that?

1521
01:26:49,122 --> 01:26:51,875
What's the point of more time of this?

1522
01:26:52,792 --> 01:26:54,460
Because I love you.

1523
01:26:56,546 --> 01:26:58,715
I've always loved you.

1524
01:26:59,674 --> 01:27:01,718
And this is a chance for us.

1525
01:27:02,427 --> 01:27:04,304
But if you pick up
that damn hammer again,

1526
01:27:04,387 --> 01:27:06,097
then that chance is gone.

1527
01:27:18,067 --> 01:27:19,485
It's your choice, Jane.

1528
01:27:20,445 --> 01:27:22,280
But I'd regret it every single day

1529
01:27:22,363 --> 01:27:23,489
if I didn't ask you to stay here

1530
01:27:23,573 --> 01:27:25,533
so we could try and figure
this out together.

1531
01:27:28,661 --> 01:27:30,705
You better come back to me.

1532
01:27:31,456 --> 01:27:33,416
I'm coming back as soon as I can.

1533
01:27:35,919 --> 01:27:38,546
- Break a leg.
- I'll break all his legs.

1534
01:27:51,976 --> 01:27:53,144
Remember that the Gate to Eternity

1535
01:27:53,227 --> 01:27:54,228
is at the literal centre

1536
01:27:54,312 --> 01:27:55,438
- of the universe.
- Universe. Yes.

1537
01:27:55,521 --> 01:27:56,856
If you go past the cluster of comets...

1538
01:27:56,940 --> 01:27:57,941
Yes, yes, I know. We've been over this.

1539
01:27:58,024 --> 01:27:59,108
I'm not gonna get lost.

1540
01:27:59,651 --> 01:28:02,320
So how you feeling
with the old stab wound?

1541
01:28:02,403 --> 01:28:03,529
I think I lost my kidney.

1542
01:28:03,613 --> 01:28:05,073
- Gone completely? Ugh.
- Mm.

1543
01:28:05,156 --> 01:28:06,074
I wish I could join you,

1544
01:28:06,157 --> 01:28:07,492
but I'd probably die,

1545
01:28:07,575 --> 01:28:08,993
and that won't help get the kids back,

1546
01:28:09,077 --> 01:28:10,453
so you'll have to go alone.

1547
01:28:10,536 --> 01:28:13,623
All you have to do
is destroy that sword.

1548
01:28:13,706 --> 01:28:14,874
It's his source of power.

1549
01:28:14,958 --> 01:28:16,417
He won't survive long without it.

1550
01:28:18,461 --> 01:28:20,380
Hey. Don't die.

1551
01:28:20,463 --> 01:28:21,923
Yeah, I know.

1552
01:29:15,560 --> 01:29:17,687
Eternity.

1553
01:29:20,023 --> 01:29:21,274
Finally.

1554
01:29:35,997 --> 01:29:37,415
Come on.

1555
01:30:03,149 --> 01:30:04,150
Hey, kids.

1556
01:30:06,861 --> 01:30:08,154
I knew he'd come.

1557
01:30:08,905 --> 01:30:09,906
Go!

1558
01:30:09,989 --> 01:30:11,074
Go, kids!

1559
01:30:20,166 --> 01:30:22,919
Everyone okay? All right,
gather round. Gather round.

1560
01:30:23,503 --> 01:30:26,130
Good to see you in person, buddy.
Good to see you.

1561
01:30:37,058 --> 01:30:38,476
All right, listen up. Here's the plan.

1562
01:30:38,559 --> 01:30:40,770
We're gonna sneak our way
towards Stormbreaker,

1563
01:30:40,853 --> 01:30:42,438
being very careful not to bump

1564
01:30:42,522 --> 01:30:44,607
